    "body": "Hey could you share you `status` config? I think it you set the `success_symbol=\"\"` it should be hidden when the exit code is zero.  \r\n\r\nThis works for me: \r\n```\r\n[status]\r\nformat='-\\[[$int]($style)\\]'\r\nsuccess_symbol=''\r\nstyle=\"red\"\r\ndisabled=false\r\n```",
